				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13679269#post-4759756</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13679269/catching-up#post-4759756</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 27 Aug 2020 06:23:32 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>HarryBlank</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6479803</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well-written, well-characterized and, well, well-done! Tying all these threads together and pulling them towards something new in an introductory tale is difficult, and you've pulled it off. My metaphors are mixed as all hell now, but you get the needlepoint.</p> <p>Excited to be standing at the front of the line for a new series, I know you're going to take this great start and build on it.</p> <p><em>Harry intentionally applies as much pressure as possible.</em></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13679269#post-4759742</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13679269/catching-up#post-4759742</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 27 Aug 2020 06:04:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Grigori Karpin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558017</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>“<strong>VLADIMIR</strong>: It's the start that's difficult.<br /> <strong>ESTRAGON</strong>: You can start from anything.<br /> <strong>VLADIMIR</strong>: Yes, but you have to decide.<br /> <strong>ESTRAGON</strong>: True.”</p> <p>― <strong>Samuel Beckett</strong>, <em>Waiting for Godot</em></p> </blockquote> <p>So, this is the beginning of tale series I have been planning since I finished my first SCP. Mostly this is concerning Agent Douglas’ recovery after the events of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4712">SCP-4712</a> but opening the way for more. I’ve got two more parts in the works currently, and should be posting relatively soon. This tale canonically takes place after <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4612">SCP-4612</a> and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5512">SCP-5512</a>.</p> <p>Hopefully y’all enjoy, and I am open to hearing any thoughts.</p> <p>Rebekah is partially correct about her experience prior to this tale, she has been changed but in very subtle fashion.</p> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/grigori-karpin-s-author-page">My Author Page</a></p> <p>Critters: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6479803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998870" alt="HarryBlank" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6479803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/harryblank" >HarryBlank</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1267048&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998870" alt="Ihp" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1267048)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ihp" >Ihp</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flopmind" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6407594&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998870" alt="Flopmind" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6407594)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/flopmind" >Flopmind</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-whitney" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5252186&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998870" alt="Dr Whitney" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5252186)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-whitney" >Dr Whitney</a></span><br /> Readers: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5722579&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998870" alt="Marcelles_Raynes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5722579)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" >Marcelles_Raynes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirslash47" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6438262&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998870" alt="Sirslash47" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6438262)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirslash47" >Sirslash47</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6394107&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604998870" alt="chiifu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6394107)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" >chiifu</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etoisle" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.ph